    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"607542\">Ariel Miculas</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/Rust.20.22Token.22.20pattern/near/400215322\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I couldn't find anything about it on google, does this have pattern have a name? Are there other examples/write-ups about how to use it?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I know it under the name of branded types, but overall there are not many resources out there about it.</p>",
        "id": 400216782,
