    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"607542\">Ariel Miculas</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/Rust.20.22Token.22.20pattern/near/400216694\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>What I'm missing is how you prove you are in a specific context with the token.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You cannot construct <code>Token</code>, since the field is private. Since there is also no constructor, the author of <code>Token</code> can control when you have access to it.</p>",
