    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/Rust.20.22Token.22.20pattern/near/400217628\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>also you can ensure that the token at some point is destroyed</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>by implementing Drop on the Token?</p>",
